_sText:
SEMPER FI MARINES!  This map's colors are dedicated to the Marine Corps and proudly display the red, blue, green and gold.  Wish I had more textures and could have added more "memorabilia" to the walls like the Marine flag and US flag but I don't know how to do it.


This is a shotgun only map and played nicely with 9 bots.  Hopefully it'll flow well with real people too.
